 local council and the remaining part in the limits of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../295/470295.xml">
Mgarr</link> local council. </p>
<p>

Bidnija has good horse riding facilities and is also home of a clay pigeon shooting club. One can also find a good restaurant here which specialises in the traditional Maltese Rabbit Stew. Its small church is dedicated to the Holy Family and a  Feast is celebrated in July.</p>
